name: 透
text:
うん
着替えてきてもいい？
trans:
Yeah.
Can I go get changed now?

name: プロデューサー
text:
──え？　……ああ、構わないけど
もうちょっと喜んだり──
trans:
──Eh? ...uhh, sure, I don't mind, but──
I was thinking you'd be more happy──

name: プロデューサー
text:
──あ、こら
控室までは飾りを取らない！
trans: ──Wait! Hey! Don't start taking your accessories off before you're even in there!

name: 透
text:
ふふっ
ありがと、プロデューサー

name: 透
trans: I'm happy. For a lot of things.
